These instructions are for windows:
1. install glpk: 
	. Download the current version of GLPK for Windows from https://sourceforge.net/projects/winglpk/
	.  Unzip the file. Copy folder glpk-4.52 to "C:\Program Files\".
	.  Add "C:\Program Files\glpk-4.52\w32" for 32-bit computer the environment variable PATH
2. install Lpsolve55j
3. install javailp
4. install jpl
5. install weka
6. install gson-2.2.4.jar
